<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-3836] PDFToImage: Text missing or background box stacks over</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3836</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When I try to convert this pdf to image, with the PDFToImage example app, then the result image is incorrect. &lt;br/&gt;
Some text blocks are missing (or maybe the background color box is stack over the text).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To reproduce: &lt;br/&gt;
`java -jar pdfbox-app-3.0.0-SNAPSHOT.jar PDFToImage /tmp/doc_mock.pdf`&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks&lt;/p&gt;</description>
