                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="16059643" author="tilman" created="Thu, 22 Jun 2017 16:27:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The cause is a flaw with caching the clipping path. The intersected clipping path is the same object as the variable &quot;lastClip&quot; so PDFBox thinks it was already set.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16059649" author="jira-bot" created="Thu, 22 Jun 2017 16:36:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1799592 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1799592&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1799592&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3836&quot; title=&quot;PDFToImage: Text missing or background box stacks over&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3836&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3836&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: lastClip needs to be reset, because after intersection it is still the same object&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16059650" author="jira-bot" created="Thu, 22 Jun 2017 16:36:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1799593 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/branches/2.0&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1799593&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1799593&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3836&quot; title=&quot;PDFToImage: Text missing or background box stacks over&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3836&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3836&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: lastClip needs to be reset, because after intersection it is still the same object&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16059652" author="tilman" created="Thu, 22 Jun 2017 16:38:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Improved:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;gs-bugzilla693520.pdf: box text now invisible where the lines are&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Different:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1927&quot; title=&quot;ClassCastException: COSInteger cannot be cast to COSObject&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-1927&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-1927&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.pdf: bottom of tower statistic doesn&apos;t look as good as before on low resolution, and slightly different at high resolution. Might be rounding problem or problem with thin lines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="16059675" author="tilman" created="Thu, 22 Jun 2017 16:53:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank you for the report. A snapshot with the bug fixed is available at the bottom of this page:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://repository.apache.org/content/groups/snapshots/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfbox-app/2.0.7-SNAPSHOT/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://repository.apache.org/content/groups/snapshots/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfbox-app/2.0.7-SNAPSHOT/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16060645" author="ccouturi" created="Fri, 23 Jun 2017 09:46:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Seriously amazing, thanks Tilman!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
